Rule Configuration

Create custom rules in governance/rules.json:

```json
{
  "rules": {
    "validation": [
      {
        "id": "CUSTOM001",
        "name": "Custom Business Rule",
        "description": "Your custom rule description",
        "type": "validation",
        "processor": "check_custom_business_rule",
        "severity": "warning",
        "enabled": true,
        "parameters": {
          "custom_parameter": "value"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

